      "review_summary": "The branch adds `updatedInput` to Claude live `can_use_tool` allow responses and Codex native `PermissionRequest` allow responses, with matching focused test assertion updates.\n\nPR surface: Source +5, Tests +34. Total +39 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible: current main still emits the old Claude live allow payload, and direct Codex source inspection shows this PR's Codex `updatedInput` allow output is rejected. I did not run a live Claude Code or Codex session in this read-only review.",
